wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.IP.ZS.def: Share of tariff lines with international peaks is the share of lines in the tariff schedule with tariff rates that exceed 15 percent.
wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.IP.ZS.name: Share of tariff lines with international peaks
wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.IP.ZS.source: World Bank staff estimates using the World Integrated Trade Solution system, based on data from United Nations Conference on Trade and Development's Trade Analysis and Information System (TRAINS) database.
